houthakker 06-Mar-18 10:25 PM
is there any difference between CreateVisibilityNode and AddFOWViewer
Shush 06-Mar-18 10:43 PM
CreateVisibilityNode is linked to the ability that casts it, so it gets the caster from it and its teamnumber (edited)
i.e. you can't make an ability that grants vision to the other team with CreateVisibilityNode
while you can do that with AddFOWViewer
also (iirc) CreateVisibilityNode always is flying vision
while FOWViewer you can set whether flying vision or ground

OnIntervalThink = function(self) self.grace_state = false local units = FindUnitsInRadius(self:GetParent():GetTeamNumber(), self:GetParent():GetAbsOrigin(), nil, self:GetAbility():GetSpecialValueFor("radius"), DOTA_UNIT_TARGET_TEAM_BOTH, DOTA_UNIT_TARGET_HERO + DOTA_UNIT_TARGET_BASIC, DOTA_UNIT_TARGET_FLAG_NONE, FIND_ANY_ORDER, false) --print(self:GetRemainingTime()) if #units < self:GetAbility():GetSpecialValueFor("units") then if not self.grace_state then self:SetDuration(self:GetAbility():GetSpecialValueFor("grace_period"), true) self.grace_state = true end else self:SetDuration(-1, true) self.grace_state = false end end end
